<h2>Best brew pub: Town Hall</h2>
<p>
Town Hall is a brew pub, which means you can only get their beer at the pub. So go to the pub. It's not very far from the Westin Hotel. It's a 1.4 mile walk if you take the most direct route, 2.1 miles if you walk along the river. Protip: walk along the river on the way to Town Hall, take the direct route on the way back. They have a nice big patio if you'd like to dine outside. If you have the time, you should go to Town Hall. Make sure you order a beer that Town Hall makes (they serve others). Another protip: ask them what's in the cask, and then order one. More details at their <span class="content-link"><%= link_to "web site", "http://www.townhallbrewery.com/#contact", target: "_blank" %></span>.
</p>
