<h2>Grain Belt:</h2>
<p>You've heard of Minnesota Nice? This isn't it! The best thing about Grain Belt is their <span class="content-link"><%= link_to "sign", "http://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large-5/grain-belt-beer-sign-and-hennepin-avenue-bridge-bradley-gross.jpg", target: "_blank" %></span>. It's located on the shore of the Mississippi River near Hennepin Avenue. It's easily visible from the Hennepin Avenue bridge and from the paved walking/biking path that goes along the river. Taking a selfie in front of the Grain Belt sign is a thing. You should do it, but you shouldn't drink the beer. Google "Grain Belt Beer sign, Minneapolis, MN" for details. <span class="editors-note">(Editor's Note: This is basically the Pabst Blue Ribbon of MN. That should probably tell you everything you need to know. Full disclosure: I'm drinking a Grain Belt as I write this.)</span>
</p>

<h2>Blue Moon:</h2>
<p>Their beer is popular in the Twin Cities. But it doesn't have to be! Just say no to Blue Moon! You'll be glad you did.
